{"tid":1278376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就嚟要打一場硬仗，鬥嘅係忍痛能力","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T07:51:02.000Z","uid":137789,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a783617e54c5e264dbf2844f901c91c18450b653","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"對方必以大搜捕打擊我哋，無可避免一定會有犧牲，唔好講未被捕嘅，淨係已被捕嘅都不計其數，但大家一定要忍痛，化悲憤為力量<br />\n<br />\n而家有場必需要打嘅硬仗，我方必須以調查搜證去處罰黑警同其上級，要佢哋為佢哋嘅惡行負責，雖然朱經緯同七警大家都覺得判得少，但係都要繼續追究黑警，未知應該點起訴佢哋之前，首先逐一鎖定每一個黑警，集合所有相關罪證，起底，立案<br />\n<br />\n睇下邊面忍唔住痛先<br />\n<br />\n咁樣唔係以同伴嘅安危去燒對方嘅安危，因為唔理你追唔追究對方，對方大權在手又講到明會秋後算帳，都擺明實整死斷正嘅手足"},{"pid":"e23602412cb5097a07f8a5e975efc473391fd0e3","tid":1278376,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"登記做選民<br />\n最後今晚!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a>"},{"pid":"02a36d0adbc4234e166351a0ea897d1b3e400d8e","tid":1278376,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e23602412cb5097a07f8a5e975efc473391fd0e3","tid":1278376,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"登記做選民<br />\n最後今晚!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:37:54.000Z","msg":"麵仔好勤力，加油！"},{"pid":"26d55295431bef7a3ee774d5bf52d5b72a7d6240","tid":1278376,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"[做實事既入黎] 鳩post收皮，實幹post整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1277959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1277959</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ead08065dbe0a5d69f200f13eac7222f6493859","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"太慢喇，對家出牌幾快手"},{"pid":"dfc183dd80e5f679fa6f66404ce7660a7defe5f0","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"繼續努力"},{"pid":"f899d4d1d6123db3760294b5a8de37db3ee8ba23","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"攻擊係最佳嘅防守"},{"pid":"822ef8db3d54bb50b15d54c761166ac2687a979c","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:34:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c90c13a2d8e27fb4fd661de4f3bacb00c01fb7e9","tid":1278376,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩女警疑於社交平台煽動他人犯罪<br />\n<a href=\"http://mango01.club/view3/4799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmango01.club%2Fview3%2F4799&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=4910984e\" target=\"_blank\">http://mango01.club/view3/4799</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ATXR1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ATXR1Q.png&h=9ec67d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李力持教唆示威者圍中聯辦禮賓府 被Cap圖知衰急刪帖<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190703/59785001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785001&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=60fd2205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785001&h=17b3b172\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190703/59785001</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDq7uOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDq7uOK.png&h=a91e43d3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d9f67b77b372fbebffd8a5ffafbfdb7a740c3c03","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c90c13a2d8e27fb4fd661de4f3bacb00c01fb7e9","tid":1278376,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩女警疑於社交平台煽動他人犯罪<br />\n<a href=\"http://mango01.club/view3/4799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmango01.club%2Fview3%2F4799&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=4910984e\" target=\"_blank\">http://mango01.club/view3/4799</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ATXR1Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ATXR1Q.png&h=9ec67d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李力持教唆示威者圍中聯辦禮賓府 被Cap圖知衰急刪帖<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190703/59785001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785001&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=60fd2205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190703%2F59785001&h=17b3b172\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190703/59785001</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PDq7uOK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPDq7uOK.png&h=a91e43d3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"斥港警侵人權　「匿名者」黑客披露逾 600 警個人資料　網罪科調查<br />\n<br />\n 6 月 12 日金鐘警民衝突期間，警方打壓示威者的手段引來爭議。有自稱知名黑客組織「匿名者」（Anonymous）的人士，近日在網上披露超過 600 名香港警員的個人資料，批評警方打壓異見、侵犯人權。警方則譴責有關行為，案件已交由網絡安全及科技罪案調查科跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》記者找到涉事網頁，可見當中存有超過 600 名警員的個人資料，包括中英文姓名、手提電話號碼，以及其住址。<br />\n<br />\n網頁製作者自稱屬於知名黑客組織「匿名者」（Anonymous），稱過去幾年一直關注著香港警方，批評警方打壓異見、暴力犯罪、侵犯人權，甚至出動槍支等武器，顯然違反《海牙公約》和《日內瓦公約》。<br />\n<br />\n「匿名者」稱今次做法是為了香港市民及人類的福祉，而決定公開部分警員的名單，警告若警方繼續犯罪，將會向公眾公開全部警方成員的資料，「你不能永遠戰勝憤怒的群眾。你選擇的方法，以及你的虛偽，已經敲響了喪鐘」。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日透過FB回應指，指案件已交由網絡安全及科技罪案調查科跟進調查。警方指，若有人以不法手段獲得個人資料，或在未經資料使用者同意下披露任何個人資料，已經可能干犯刑事罪行。警方再次強烈譴責這類型行為，強調會積極調查每一個個案並跟進到底。<br />\n<br />\n此外警方昨晚發佈長四分幾鐘的影片，警務處支援部助理處長林曉彤提及，近日有超過 500 名警員及親友被人在網上「起底」，更有人到警察人員親友的工作地點作滋擾。警方強烈譴責欺凌行為，已設立 24 小時熱線給警方人員舉報，並將超過 120 宗「起底」個案轉交私隱專員公署跟進。她警告，若事件涉及刑事成分，如刑事恐嚇，警方將會徹查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%A5%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E4%BE%B5%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A-%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E8%80%85-%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E9%80%BE-600-%E8%AD%A6%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E7%B6%B2%E7%BD%AA%E7%A7%91%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E5%258C%25BF%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%2580%25BE-600-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=e69a6a7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E5%258C%25BF%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%2580%25BE-600-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%25A7%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%2F&h=d5085df2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%96%A5%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E4%BE%B5%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A-%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E8%80%85-%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E9%80%BE-600-%E8%AD%A6%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-%E7%B6%B2%E7%BD%AA%E7%A7%91%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"70a260b2c969d3512c3147b35e3ce95a7cc4302c","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxpphG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxpphG6.jpg&h=1306622f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RZcUWC2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRZcUWC2.png&h=36132f3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"790ef9ea8e75433eabb98628426a98f52795be85","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"大追捕已經開始<br />\n<br />\n當我們仍執著於抗爭暴力的倫理分析，大追捕已經開始了。今天為香港前仆後繼的年輕人們，要麼被打至頭破血流，要麼被告至鋃鐺入獄。<br />\n<br />\n「暴力就是暴力」？<br />\n<br />\n如果我們不能容忍暴力，就更不能容忍如今殺紅了眼的警察。他們揮動警棍、發射子彈，不是為了除暴安良、保護市民，而是出於獸性大發、仇恨作崇。我們的教育到底何曾說過，執法就是真理、穿上制服就能為所欲為？<br />\n<br />\n就在寫下這段話的同時，旺角街頭的市民被穿著便服、大喊「同我隻揪呀」的警察按地圍毆，打得血流滿面。即使我們看不見無形的制度暴力、政治壓迫，最起碼也應有生而為人的良知：濫用警權，就是赤裸裸的暴力！<br />\n<br />\n不要再自欺欺人了。「暴力就是暴力」，我們沒有任何理由，要再給這些自願成為國家機器的暴警，予以同情的理解。<br />\n<br />\n「接受法律制裁」？<br />\n<br />\n放心，六月過後，為香港背水一戰的年輕人即將面對審判，在獄中押上青春，一如此刻身陷囹圄的戴耀廷、梁天琦。<br />\n<br />\n倘若我們感受過他們在催淚彈下堅定的吶喊、在立法會外熾烈的眼神，就知道這些無名者不是第一個以身犯險，也決不會是最後一個。只要問題核心一日懸而未決，仍然會有千萬個後來者負隅頑抗，在絕望中採取更激烈的表達手法。 <br />\n<br />\n一旦爭取成功，獲益的是全香港的福祉；倘若失敗，接下來將要犧牲服刑的卻是這些年輕人，而不是安守家中、坐享其成的我們。擅闖議會固然非法，我們大可繼續隔岸觀火，否定前線的衝擊。但難道現在的檢控真的只是為了擊碎玻璃、塗鴉區徽的行為嗎？<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖籠罩<br />\n<br />\n透過犧牲年輕世代，政權正是要殺一儆百，製造白色恐怖，嚇退所有參與過反送中運動的人：一百萬、二百萬個在遊行隊伍中的你，六一二在金鐘親歷催淚彈的你，七月六日在屯門區大展旗鼓掃黃的你，七月七日第一次為遊行踏足九龍區的你。<br />\n<br />\n過去一個月來，穿黑衫要擔心被截查，在網上發言要擔心被追蹤，夜半在家亦要擔心警方上門秋後算帳。若說香港已是不折不扣的警察國家 (police state)，亦不為過。<br />\n<br />\n在白色恐怖籠罩的當下，我們要加入分裂、譴責的行列，讓公民社會一沉百踩、萬劫不覆，抑或要避免五年前雨傘運動的創傷，與豁出去的年輕人憂戚與共、進退一同？<br />\n<br />\n我們已無路可退<br />\n<br />\n在你繼續批評年輕人衝動魯莽、少不更事之前，願你能夠進入他們的世界，看見警察的無法無天、政權的專橫霸道，感受前路只有被打與被捕的絕望。<br />\n<br />\n大追捕已經開始，漫長的審判在前方靜候。然而，約翰‧羅爾斯說過，「最終的審判不在於法庭，不在於行政機關，不在於立法機關，而在於我們每一位市民」(&ldquo;The final court of appeal is not the court, nor the executive, nor the legislature, but the electorate as a whole&rdquo;)。<br />\n<br />\n寧鳴而死、不默而生，香港人已無路可退。我們唯有團結一致，才能見證：歷史終將站在正義一方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bCzgVKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbCzgVKE.jpg&h=06684f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVrOMRr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVrOMRr.jpg&h=c53696bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=869203260125037&amp;id=869054420139921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D869203260125037%26id%3D869054420139921&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPrScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=68e30071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=869203260125037&amp;id=869054420139921</a>"},{"pid":"4fdc4269ca9c89e954ec68cb4a2a6ee147cc35dd","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"做嘢喇"},{"pid":"6881643defa436e0cfa084584057b3a33f460670","tid":1278376,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"[經典重溫] 日本學生擊敗防暴警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310573</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9129473649f39eee42e9b9c6ba153d0006b6b05e","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a124f91c4bc9da76e5811b3625d89cdfc7e02e7","tid":1278376,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"日日係咁拉人，又即刻開記者會，根本係挑機"}]}